snippet.title: Super Bear Adventure - Nintendo Switch™ Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Bear Adventure is now available for Nintendo Switch™ on the Nintendo eShop!

Get Super Bear Adventure on the eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/super-bear-adventure-switch/

Get Super Bear Adventure for iPhone and iPad on the App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1531842415
Get Super Bear Adventure for Android on the Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Earthkwak.Platformer

More on https://superbearadventure.com
Game made by Stéphane Hulot

Nintendo Switch is a trademark of Nintendo.
